{"tid":2183896,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵督導證8.31警阻救護入站","createTime":"2020-09-01T08:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T08:19:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"966528f3661cb5b0909afe0c04dd5ddaa8560d66","tid":2183896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/B5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FB5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7ggLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=6544dded\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FB5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA%2F&h=32c1391b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/B5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港鐵督導證8.31警阻救護入站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rvZPw_OAeWnEQP0NRzgXmozJgLg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MRXDU4AWBHMTJ6BPZFZQ2DJD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrvZPw_OAeWnEQP0NRzgXmozJgLg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MRXDU4AWBHMTJ6BPZFZQ2DJD4.jpg&h=208b95a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「Lunch哥」David昨在太子站悼念8.31，卻遭港鐵職員包圍及票控。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8.31，警方衝入太子站無差別恐襲乘客後，隨即驅趕記者，站內發生甚麼事無人知曉。一直以諸多理由無公開當晚所有閉路電視片段的港鐵成為眾矢之的。「眾新聞」昨報道，引述一名事發時在場的港鐵督導員，承認當時港鐵與警方關係緊張，「完全摸唔透佢哋」，並確認有警員藉詞阻撓救護員入站急救傷者。<br />\n<br />\n該名港鐵職員以化名「T先生」接受眾新聞訪問，言談間把8.31恐襲責任推給警方：「我可以講返少少background，嗰段時間我哋同警察嘅關係都有少少緊張。因為點解呢，例如喺葵芳、喺太古，我哋被人圍咗好耐，後尾都冇辦法要報警，但係警察唔嚟，佢成日都話佢人手唔夠，或者係調配緊人手，所以呢嗰段時間我哋對佢哋嘅反應係無乜信心。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「完全摸唔透佢哋」<br />\n<br />\nT先生續說：「自從元朗7.21事件，有一段好長時間，其實我哋係完全摸唔透佢哋（警方）幾時出嚟幾時唔出嚟。所以，我哋。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞引述T先生當晚在太子站大堂的反應，「我一去到大堂，其實就見到好驚訝嘅畫面，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n8.31另一焦點在於救護人員被警方阻延入站施救，T先生證實：「守喺出口嘅嗰個警察，又係非常之stubborn，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他續說：「事後。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a76aee7b6d1b898042e1eeaa58e895f8a9af8769","tid":2183896,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"如果呢件事我哋早啲知道嘅話，係消防處嘅救護員，你理得佢處理咩case，你開閘畀佢落嚟咪得囉，諗咁多做咩嘢啫。<br />\n<br />\n如果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無如果呀 你地成班都係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}